sub_title: Event & Marketing specialist reinforced with a strong Administrative background
summary: 10+ years experienced specialist in Event & Marketing reinforced with a strong Administrative background, efficient communication and leadership skills, accompanied by an outstanding track record of event organization. I have successfully influenced the positive transformation of several local and international projects across Europe and Eurasia. My team and I have consistently worked with our in-business executive partners to deliver cost savings and elevate the culture of performance. Self-starter, strong planner and problem solver who readily adapts to change, works independently and exceeds expectations.
